{"tid":1904623,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【氣象】（2020年3月上旬）一股清勁東北季風及其補充將為華南帶來清涼的天氣，中期有幾陣雨","createTime":"2020-02-29T17:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T02:10:41.000Z","uid":38255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3fb6ffe1f9ddcc388ae9e52b398f329a0c570a","tid":1904623,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:51:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><img src=\"http://x.co/wk014\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk014&h=14c2415a&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>氣象討論：2020年3月上旬</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2020年3月1日至10日</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。 當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。 為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請關注<span style=\"color: red;\">氣象巴打&bull;高登氣象台</span>最新動態<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/z4brcbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fz4brcbr.png&h=d512611e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/2v9xh70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2v9xh70.png&h=7ef830e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgnzQsWS.png&h=54316817&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/7sNQ3N2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F7sNQ3N2.png&h=15a63bfa&s={SIZE}\" /></span></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤溫度術語</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒      ≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷      8 - 12 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">清涼    13 - 17 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和暖／稍涼 18 - 22 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫暖    23 - 27 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">炎熱    28 - 32 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">酷熱      ≧ 33 &deg;C</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_webcam_uc.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e783fe16\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 天氣雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fradars%2Fradarc_range1.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=8a2d0b51\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm</a><br />\n◆ 機場天氣預報：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Faviat%2Ftaf_decode.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=b400eba6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm</a><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=2d2e4725\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=6eefcac6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftextonly%2Fexplain%2Fintroc.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9cda5133\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 短期氣候預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fseason%2Fseasonc.htm&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=af2678d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm</a><br />\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=0a5669b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qQj8Xe\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qqyU9G\" /><br />\n▲ 實時天氣照片<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qPKaOw\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qu5ZAb\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2sLVc4U\" /><br />\n▲ 本港分區氣溫／相對濕度／海平面氣壓<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2pSLUlJ\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2rqtOIV\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2rdU6AS\" /><br />\n▲ 風向及風速／陣風／能見度<br />\n<img src=\"http://m.weather.gov.hk/image/radar_scale.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.weather.gov.hk%2Fimage%2Fradar_scale.jpg&h=087d95fd&s={SIZE}\" />　　<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_256_320/rad256_6.jpg\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_128_320/rad128_6.jpg\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_064_320/rad064_6.jpg\" /><br />\n▲ 香港256／128／64公里雷達<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2a5ticH\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2ahInaZ\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統</strong>"},{"pid":"6c75810f78b319be81278b1b89b138520bec3bfb","tid":1904623,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png&h=fae8adfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png&h=60556b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png&h=85440aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png&h=27f79c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGW （gale warning)-由日本氣象廳發出，意思係24小時內會有熱帶風暴形成，即係估計24小時內命名<br />\nTCFA (tropical cyclone formation alert)-由JTWC發出，指24小時會有熱帶氣旋（包括熱帶低氣壓）生成，即24小時內正式編號升格<br />\nFFS-美國全球預報系統(GFS)的俗稱，諷刺其計算結果如同FF，但近一年預報準確度有所提升<br />\nCPA TO HK-該風暴與本港之最接近距離<br />\nJTWC BIN C之旅-收集每報JTWC預報報文中的CPA TO HK，事後可以實際CPA TO HK對照作BIN C之用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馮瑞權-澳門氣象局前局長<br />\n風水權-馮瑞權俗稱<br />\n風水靜，神婆靜，作法靜，巫婆靜-前任澳門氣象局副局長梁嘉靜俗稱，現為首席顧問高級技術員，一度停職4個月。<br />\n赤的疑惑-高登氣象台台長<br />\n七長官/7長官-製作氣象台警報gif會員<br />\nRose-製作高登風格天氣警告圖的會員，其作品並不授予連登使用<br />\n楊振權副庭長-Baroclinic於高登的最新名字<br />\n桜の抹茶刺身-連登氣象post負責人1<br />\n道地檸檬綠茶-連登氣象post負責人2<br />\n雪菜肉絲炆米-連登颱風航空交通post負責人<br />\n一個地球人-連登中仔細分析颱風走向及其他高空氣象圖的高質會員<br />\n當榴蓮遇上芒果-連登中另一位氣象知識豐富的高質會員<br />\n逝去的不回來/夏天冬天夏天-知名氣溫體感假膠，有去埋其他台派膠既attention seeker<br />\n李棟旭-連登中製作大量有趣的氣象post相關改圖的會員（包括以上四幅術語圖）<br />\n南珠隻狗-連登中氣象知識亦較豐富的會員<br />\n伊甸園菜肉餃-伊甸園市長在連登的最新名字<br />\nXXXXXX堅豎-土豆在連登的分身<br />\n力場J-貼出李首富照片並提醒各巴絲記得準時返工的會員<br />\nDH-direct hit 本港一百公里內掠過<br />\n中出-風暴中心直接橫過本港<br />\n貓5- cat5 五級颱風的英文簡稱<br />\n五隻貓-同上，有cat1-5<br />\n醉警-酷熱天氣警告誤字<br />\n南海之王-氣象迷對香港天文台的尊稱，指其對南海熱帶氣旋預測表現良好，但只限接近廣東沿岸的南海部份，因此又被稱為南海北部之王<br />\nSTNR-滯留不動<br />\nN0.1-向北移0.1度，/E/S/W（東/南/西）同理<br />\n8中X-天文台指定8個測風站中有X個達標<br />\nlogin-登陸，源於cctvb錯將&Prime;登陸&Prime;打成&Prime;登錄&Prime;<br />\nlogin password-由上引申之術語，意指登陸地<br />\n近岸爆發-熱帶氣旋在靠近沿岸時急劇增強，令沿岸地區威脅大增<br />\n0號觀望訊號-香港傳媒於熱帶氣旋仍末形成時，已大肆吹奏香港會打風；又或熱帶氣旋已形成，但並非採取接近本港之路徑，傳媒卻仍吹奏有機會打風。此詞用於諷刺傳媒猶如代替天文台發出熱帶氣旋警告訊號<br />\n(香港)暴雨走廊-指大嶼山東北起，經荃青葵，擴展至沙田大埔一段，因西南水汽易受此一帶地型抬升影響較易有暴雨。靈感來自美國「龍捲風走廊」。以下為經典例子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=33884fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e80d38ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為一分鐘風速標準，轉化至十分鐘標準（hko,jma標準）請乘0.93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nchan ho.jpg-副檔名可以改為任意三個不同英文字，為伊甸園市長愛用圖片，即下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c1ebcd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下圖為兩登氣象台提及峴港時愛用cap圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5d8a07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d068c84f4f01c8020e601acb05cf9688c4c5e04d","tid":1904623,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"今日最高28℃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f405d2878e507819022c088ae929f3a3388e0e7","tid":1904623,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d068c84f4f01c8020e601acb05cf9688c4c5e04d","tid":1904623,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"今日最高28℃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"我感覺好似炒咗高溫,唔好話28 <br />\n<br />\n26都未必有"},{"pid":"08d1a8aa5385d50dd696c3b60e60a20a750091b4","tid":1904623,"uid":162037,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"6f405d2878e507819022c088ae929f3a3388e0e7","tid":1904623,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d068c84f4f01c8020e601acb05cf9688c4c5e04d","tid":1904623,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"今日最高28℃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"我感覺好似炒咗高溫,唔好話28 <br />\n<br />\n26都未必有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"有26.6度既唔似啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今日真心涼到入心入肺<img src=\"/assets